RTRS - Hockey - Australia beaten 3 - 1 by India in Champions Trophy . Result of a round - robin league match in the Champions Trophy hockey tournament on Wednesday . India beat Australia 3 - 1 ( halftime 0 - 1 ) Scorers : India - Ramandeep Singh 40 and 42 , Gavin Fereira 47 . Australia - Jay Tacy 6 . 
